author: Adam Voge
title: Former TOLD exec pitches townhomes along I-394
text:
Home / News / Construction & Development / Former TOLD exec pitches townhomes along I-394 Melrose Development is proposing 70 rental townhomes in two- and three-story buildings just south of Interstate 394 in St. Louis Park. (Submitted rendering) Former TOLD exec pitches townhomes along I-394 By: Adam Voge July 24, 2015 3:52 pm 0 The city of St. Louis Park has closed on two parcels along Wayzata Boulevard and the interstate and simultaneously flipped them to Melrose Development.
